title: Lemony Chicken Paillard with Sweet Potato Wedges, Arugula Salad, and Chimichurri
description: We’ve marinated butterflied chicken breasts with lemon and shallot for a bright burst of flavor.  Smoky sweet potato wedges are complimented by a peppery arugula salad for contrast. The dish is finished with our favorite condiment—an Argentine-inspired chimichurri sauce!
